  "logNo": "222979123291",
  "title": "이수한의원 의료진 세미나 &quot;Nerve Hydrodissection Technique을 활용한 초음파 영상 유도하 약침시술&quot;",
  "addDate": "2023. 1. 9.",
  "categoryNo": "43",
  "parentCategoryNo": "1",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=222979123291",
  "html_size": 211940,
  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-89d376c3-bc03-4e29-97b7-021ad02b2014\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4a353853-3d20-4a5d-9958-3f517ce1a1a3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-da721028-88fc-45fe-a6ce-9da183657d58\">안녕하세요. 이수한의원입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6b690bf7-0647-4074-a85c-5d36d5c17791\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-52539724-c557-4b46-8da3-47af9e20b480\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7129f404-8771-4a23-8872-fdfc35f6a6a3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e40fc2af-f3f5-482a-ab4e-a26dbedbba2c\">이수한의원 문학진원장, 나효석원장, 이윤호원장과 외부의 몇 원장님들이 모여서 수년째 세미나를 이어오고 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-48eca04f-25d9-4f1c-b69f-976de0c2f2ea\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2fc1f31a-9790-417d-b564-4233a7fcaa62\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-570f63b4-2d56-44c2-bb4b-c31c10ca3b35\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-095d6619-3028-4c75-91ef-e76873b291c0\">새로운 의학지식과 치료기술의 습득, 질병의 최신지견 등을 함께 학습하고 치료방법을 시연하고 익히는 세미나 시간입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a7c8de53-ac27-4c1d-8184-c7b61b55a30f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7918dbeb-499d-4d0f-9e44-60c704bb7050\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-03810c2f-3d24-4152-be07-6257bf1b4e7e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9fc89ab3-8bf0-4e84-8bc9-33817f1248c6\">1월 8일에, 2023년 첫 번째 세미나를 진행했습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4f4ac29c-0efb-4663-8f64-9e15c81f3a61\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c6fb12a1-f7f5-4c44-a777-75367603e35a\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0f16a11b-23b5-494a-ab87-5770d783fbc2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-80835d74-136e-4952-9546-dc70b75977a3\">2022년 말에 대법원에서 한의사의 초음파기기 사용은 적법하다는 판결이 있었습니다. 그에 따라 이수한의원에서도 초음파기기를 도입하고 사용할 준비를 하고 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-bf52f781-6a09-4301-82a9-78a1eeda4625\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f710104c-b871-42d1-b55e-a3d47bed5009\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d8974438-6646-4e01-a155-2738559999e4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7ef833e0-5d0f-42c1-af91-7aa3e2ca2682\">남성역 앞 이수한의원 의료진은 내원환자분의 증상 및 병력에 맞춰 적합한 이학적 검사를 꼼꼼히 시행하여 진단을 해왔었는데, 이제  초음파를 활용해서 관절, 신경, 혈관, 인대, 힘줄 등의 상태를 확인하면 보다 더 정확한 진단을 내리는데 큰 도움이 될겁니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ca11062c-d937-4bcc-bb29-3391646990fd\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-56e983e6-e113-4448-b58b-255f23ea01bd\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f771534f-c1c2-4689-99a8-411cc7ac3df1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d726ae96-45f8-4ff1-840f-799c43c94db3\">뿐만 아니라 침 또는 약침을 시술할때 초음파 영상을 보면서 시술을 하게 된다면 훨씬 정확하고 효과적인 시술이 가능하고 그만큼 치료 효과도 좋아질 것으로 기대됩니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-afffcf7f-769d-4533-b289-74d0a1f25a09\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-98a050ee-85d3-4b96-87b2-775af476f54e\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-fffb320a-5eeb-4d2e-8549-3ae8a3d9eb34\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-fffb320a-5eeb-4d2e-8549-3ae8a3d9eb34\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/839b259bd6c7c049.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"680\", \"originalHeight\" : \"279\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/839b259bd6c7c049.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/839b259bd6c7c049.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"205\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-41c415f9-0c45-4011-96c9-4e1654a4a41f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-32fded41-5936-4609-8108-ab4890d2dc01\"><a href=\"https://www.frontiersin.org/articles/10.3389/fneur.2019.00216/full\" class=\"se-link\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.frontiersin.org/articles/10.3389/fneur.2019.00216/full</a></span></p></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4b197fa3-5a78-45f2-82bd-ac2503b5c5d5\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d6eb699b-cd03-450c-a8cf-343f3c2580c6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a78c0966-d2c5-476b-9de5-c5416a982d1b\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-975ee4e5-7e97-41c1-86e9-b7294a1616e7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b083912a-3fee-46e5-bd13-df361f338527\">Nerve Hydrodissection Technique 이란 말이 생소하시죠?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-82674355-9df7-4242-83de-8f80a14f75d2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a785e608-8d16-4a48-8d10-6b1baf96f54e\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-be2d73d1-8b03-41b8-9dab-01920f88ac5b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-83fa78c6-906a-4b82-9fae-9379639ca87b\">Nerve hydrodissection (HD) is a technique which uses high-resolution ultrasound-guided fluid injection to separate nerves from a surrounding or adjacent structure, usually the fascia, which is believed to constrict or irritate the nerve either during movement or at rest.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-bcecb1ee-40ef-412d-bb7f-8cd6c937db06\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8b535c77-db89-425f-bccc-8c8e8e7f63ae\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1a1ddbe8-b4ed-421c-95ca-178b667a2bb0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5a15f553-421b-48bd-a0e3-9c8c64b17558\">&quot;Ultrasound-Guided Nerve Hydrodissection for Pain Management:  An Updated Review of Anatomy and Techniques/ Lam et al. Feb 2020&quot; 이란 논문에는 위와같이 정의를 내리고 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9f362829-7120-4374-87c9-946e96b5640c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-53cdaa79-e770-4268-98e5-e54cacef9b77\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-49933d5d-b406-4800-afe4-c638f54d606c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8167a605-2448-4661-836d-7304ac592bf2\">간단히 설명하자면</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-783c7629-7147-4dbd-bb10-c2f810f1ac91\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-97f441cc-db28-49d9-9fdf-930739ccf2bc\">초음파 영상을 보면서 주변 조직에 의해 눌려있는 신경을 분리시켜 치료하는 방법입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ce84b1eb-3fe1-4336-877a-b5ab38c071a4\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:395px;\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-ce84b1eb-3fe1-4336-877a-b5ab38c071a4\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/23b617e09e2dd781.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"395\", \"originalHeight\" : \"395\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/23b617e09e2dd781.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/23b617e09e2dd781.jpg\" data-width=\"395\" data-height=\"395\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a979a860-cc61-42a4-9940-e5c529046082\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c3665acc-f52b-4e65-93f1-62f48b9c07a9\"><a href=\"https://zh-cn.facebook.com/sonoskills/posts/nerve-hydrodissection-is-a-technique-used-when-treating-peripheral-nerve-entrapm/2669563626435610/\" class=\"se-link\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh-cn.facebook.com/sonoskills/posts/nerve-hydrodissection-is-a-technique-used-when-treating-peripheral-nerve-entrapm/2669563626435610/</a></span></p></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-cc1374ac-7eed-422f-9715-0f9d692c828c\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8205bcbe-d3f5-4c70-bf01-10fef77f074f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-aadfff16-2d64-4fa0-bee7-6a4a53f9cded\">디스크가 신경을 누르면 허리가 아프고 다리가 저리는 등의 디스크 증상이 생기잖아요? </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-27da4e3a-c90a-48ca-9be9-8651551b96e3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4697768d-28f5-4f5c-8724-8a7fb48e653e\">허리 뿐 아니라 몸 어느 곳에서든지 어떤 원인에 의해서 신경이 눌리게 되면 다양한 증상이 나타나게 됩니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9071a88c-1e9d-4d7f-9842-bccda9813593\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f3be1784-fe64-4ca4-a68d-3237eed44d84\">저린다. 시리다. 아프다. 땡긴다. 스물스물 벌레가 기어다니는 것 같다. 힘이 없다. 화끈거린다. 결린다. 뻐근하다. 무겁다. 등등 매우 다양한 증상이 나타날 수 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b8451dc3-bafd-49fa-91c4-b10848ab3d74\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f7082121-4a09-42d9-904b-74f7a848f703\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-bd6d0f30-66e3-4ba1-9c75-b92110b72654\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1935fa9f-5c68-4246-922e-c5e3cefc178c\">증상을 듣고, 병력을 확인한 후 원인이 신경이 눌려서 생긴 것으로 추정이 되면 여러가지 이학적검사(여기저기 눌러보거나 움직여 보는 등 신체를 진찰하는 방법)를 통해 진단을 정확하게 내리게 됩니다. 여기에 더해서 초음파로 확인을 하면 더 선명하게 확인할 수 있습니다. 이때 초음파 영상으로 원인을 확인하기만 하는게 아니라 바로 눈으로 보면서 치료까지 진행을 하는거죠.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-14957480-7491-4488-8f6f-4968ab76a186\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-282a29c7-5aa4-4f90-bb6b-0ace70d2a1e3\">신경이 눌린 부위로 주사기 바늘을 정확하게 위치시킨 후 그 부위에 주사액을 쏘아주면 눌렸던 신경 주위로 주사액이 퍼져나가면서 주변 조직에 눌려있던 신경을 되살려 주게 됩니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7c870220-ffe7-44f0-b8e1-2642f1cd0f06\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-390a8563-84b2-4f27-844c-05cc841ae983\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9c1b7a8a-0927-4462-96af-73486bc9f88a\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:298px;\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-9c1b7a8a-0927-4462-96af-73486bc9f88a\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6823bcabf0d013ef.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"298\", \"originalHeight\" : \"169\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6823bcabf0d013ef.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6823bcabf0d013ef.jpg\" data-width=\"298\" data-height=\"169\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-315acea8-df7e-4e53-8a4a-f22f072a2704\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3d7c1380-3ce5-4587-8cbd-290dbf77abdf\"><a href=\"https://zh-cn.facebook.com/sonoskills/posts/nerve-hydrodissection-is-a-technique-used-when-treating-peripheral-nerve-entrapm/2669563626435610/\" class=\"se-link\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh-cn.facebook.com/sonoskills/posts/nerve-hydrodissection-is-a-technique-used-when-treating-peripheral-nerve-entrapm/2669563626435610/</a></span></p></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c341e436-fd53-4f8f-8b0d-ab6af43ba339\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-057446dd-a5c9-4bd2-a4df-f3e1b82a520f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-334a7661-5e13-4ea3-9445-9a3a54f2b8b0\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-749e43d7-e66d-4958-95c0-9126898069e6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-585fec00-70d4-419a-8b17-e236683e992a\">이수한의원에서는 Nerve Hydrodissection Technique 을 사용하여 치료할 때 스테로이드나 국소마취제, 소염진통제 등을 사용하지 않고 &#x27;약침액&#x27;을 이용해서 치료 합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-780aac7a-ec36-4864-87d7-1cbec3de5ca8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c32662cd-ec96-4926-a862-c8483a347873\">그래서</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-fa2a67b9-2605-4bdb-bc19-6dac2481a95c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f34bcfc8-529b-42a6-a627-d572c961b544\">&quot;Nerve Hydrodissection Technique을 활용한 초음파 영상 유도하 약침시술&quot;</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4931726c-0a8c-4ae6-bb66-f145e28c96b5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2103a921-a13a-4cb5-b602-8c4ddf6cb3c3\">입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c9c2e4c3-ad17-4aa5-baa6-afaa093d89de\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5d08e06a-f855-46c7-836b-f317f49c1aa4\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c394500a-bf5f-4c01-8677-2cc9466ac316\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0c956689-ccf5-459b-ae73-c5c121e84c82\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c5475154-47a2-410f-bf5f-43a1d1063f4d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3d3594ca-edf4-468d-982c-34227c34c03c\">초음파 영상 유도하 약침시술 기법은 추나요법과 함께 시술할때 훨씬 더 좋습니다. 신경이 눌린 것을 치료하는데서 멈추는게 아니고, 신경이 눌리게 된 원인까지 추나요법으로 교정을 해주면 더욱 좋겠죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-037b3542-4a7c-4656-8351-089a9b7d9f9d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-abb11d09-5ba1-4c57-ae11-2256562f5cce\">신경이 눌리는 원인은 잘못된 움직임, 반복적인 사용, 나쁜 자세, 틀어진 골반척추, 신경 주변의 근육긴장 등이니 추나요법으로 치료해주면 재발을 막고 증상을 예방할 수 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-551830fa-1b43-4ed0-baab-74bdd1598c16\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4933e81a-8509-4fd7-ab26-8d427db2e9da\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f1b7e23e-87a4-4a07-b988-fe539661d961\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6d3f2311-b0c3-44ed-ba17-350fa4ea822d\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-695809b5-8199-48d0-905a-fe5128dc8c9d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-bc129d09-96fc-4f27-bac1-22785a64144c\">이수한의원 의료진은 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b406c59b-3d1c-4c10-99c9-9347e75078b6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4ab19f57-7a6c-4f28-9165-5f10b691e57e\">더 나은 치료법과 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ef0351c6-07dc-4654-a689-4b53c1408e64\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-32e16ca9-4795-4d5b-b166-fbb2a2286823\">더 좋은 치료효과를 위해 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-bf169214-eff5-4943-a194-6bdb2413e33d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e35239c2-ed1b-4d0f-bdc9-56901000f436\">항상 노력하고 연구하고 있으니</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7611c711-c669-4a15-a046-f637b877c962\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ae77b9bb-49c0-4696-a3da-7a637d1f961e\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2f26db31-db64-4996-a570-77212d9341b3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-08c44b33-9774-4856-b9c8-cff8e5298e20\">병이 있으면 미루지 말고 이수한의원에 내원하셔서 치료 받으세요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-24c3b2a7-713c-4a3e-bedf-51975780b8db\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d98802b6-e412-4cc5-9035-138ed1fbff7f\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2bb23402-1b1d-